name: Barakat Mubarak Mabrook
bio: [('Beginning', 'He began athletics in 2006. (tooofa.com, 23 Jul 2018)'), ('Reason', 'He initially played football until age 18, when his coach suggested he try sprinting. Later, I was sent to a training camp in Europe by the Oman Athletic Association." (omanobserver.om, 23 Nov 2010; SportsDeskOnline, 16 Aug 2018)SANCTIONHe tested positive for the banned substance methylprednisolone at the 2011 Arab Games in Doha, Qatar. bio: [('Beginning', 'She began playing tennis at age four in Muscat, Oman. (Athlete, 02 Oct 2014)'), ('Reason', 'She was introduced to the sport by her mother.
